<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>قَالَ الْجَدُّ وَلَمْ أَقِفْ عَلَيْهِ بِهَذَا / اللَّفْظِ وَهُوَ فِي مَعْنَى<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٤٤٣ - مَا وَقَى الْمَرْءُ بِهِ عِرْضَهُ فَهُوَ صَدَقَةٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٤٤٤ - الْمَرْءُ بِسَعْدِهِ لَا بِأَبِيهِ وَجَدِّهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٤٤٥ - الْمَرْءُ مَحْمُولٌ عَلَى نِيَّتِهِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>لَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ وَهُوَ فِي مَعْنَى <span class="c1">" إِنَّمَا الأَعْمَالُ بِالنِّيَّاتِ "</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>